{"tid":774853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7歲女孩越長越醜 家長懷疑非親生 真相是......","createTime":"2018-08-10T16:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T04:32:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6988952470f6f03def4d30abe582699b525d1d46","tid":774853,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】湖南長沙一對夫婦因其7歲女兒越長越難看，還越來越不像爸媽，懷疑並非親生，其父母帶她到醫院咨詢。經檢查後，發現原來女童因鼻腔內的腺樣體肥大，影響了面部發育。女童經手術切除病變組織後，相信面容會逐漸恢復。<br />\n<br />\n經湖南省第二人民醫院耳鼻喉科劉剛副主任檢查後發現，女孩牙齒外凸不齊，嘴唇厚，臉較一般小朋友要長，講話有明顯的鼻音，張口檢查發現顎骨高拱。女兒爸爸說，孩子從小睡覺就愛打鼾，並習慣張嘴呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n劉醫生經初步檢查，判斷女孩有腺樣體肥大。經過纖維鼻咽鏡檢查時，發現明顯肥大的腺樣體將其鼻咽部堵塞，因此睡覺時打鼾，並且一直張口呼吸，長期以來持續這個動作，影響了面部的發育。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，腺樣體位於人體鼻腔後端與咽部交界處，表面不平，小孩從出生後即存在，一般10歲逐漸萎縮。<br />\n<br />\n劉醫生解釋，反覆感冒、鼻腔咽部炎症反覆刺激，使3-5歲及更大一點的小孩腺樣體發生病理性增生，肥大的腺樣體可引起中耳炎、鼻炎，引起刺激性咳嗽和長期張口呼吸，影響面容的正常發育，出現上頜骨變長、顎骨高拱、牙齒不齊、上切牙突出、唇厚、缺乏表情等表現。因此，家長會看到孩子會 「越長越醜」。如果發現及時，經過手術切除肥大的腺樣體後，孩子面容會慢慢糾正。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LM5MQsC8AvRlKxWg0gZFLw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-08-10/d2612b50-9c6a-11e8-be80-7b07643549cf__2018081013135862308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLM5MQsC8AvRlKxWg0gZFLw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-08-10%2Fd2612b50-9c6a-11e8-be80-7b07643549cf__2018081013135862308.jpg&h=52de5feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/7%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E8%B6%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%B6%8A%E9%86%9C-%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E9%9D%9E%E8%A6%AA%E7%94%9F-%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E6%98%AF-051100748.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F7%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E8%25B6%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25B6%258A%25E9%2586%259C-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%259D%259E%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%2594%259F-%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2598%25AF-051100748.html&d=4wFD7zTA%2BXPgWVWBqsvoeiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6aaec03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/7%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E8%B6%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%B6%8A%E9%86%9C-%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E9%9D%9E%E8%A6%AA%E7%94%9F-%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E6%98%AF-051100748.html</a>"},{"pid":"e520fcc21cf0e629b1d8f00cd30086599100988e","tid":774853,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"以為錢七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc113037b9b650fedd82e026e37ae623c805940c","tid":774853,"uid":3976,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e520fcc21cf0e629b1d8f00cd30086599100988e","tid":774853,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"以為錢七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"但係錢七 好明顯係佢兩個親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9517a0a2c34ef182c16c0549140b334bf7e785","tid":774853,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"金鐘班連登仔要去check check"},{"pid":"a9ca5349385839dba8507eb6e065d2e1d21df511","tid":774853,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc113037b9b650fedd82e026e37ae623c805940c","tid":774853,"uid":3976,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e520fcc21cf0e629b1d8f00cd30086599100988e","tid":774853,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"以為錢七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\